
Sustainable Development Goals (SDG) Alignment

The Mul Biotech Farms Ecosystem contributes to multiple United Nations Sustainable Development Goals (SDGs) through regenerative agriculture, environmental intelligence, carbon farming, aquaculture, biodiversity conservation, climate resilience, and digital agricultural innovation.

