SDG-02| Zero Hunger| Sustainable Agriculture, Food Security, Integrated Farming
SDG-06| Clean Water and Sanitation| Water Management, Aquaculture, Water Monitoring
SDG-08| Decent Work and Economic Growth| Rural Entrepreneurship, Farmer Livelihoods, Green Jobs
SDG-09| Industry, Innovation and Infrastructure| Agri-Tech, GIS Systems, MRV Platforms, Digital Agriculture
SDG-11| Sustainable Cities and Communities| Urban Farming, Community Sustainability Programs
SDG-12| Responsible Consumption and Production| Circular Economy, Waste Valorization, Resource Efficiency
SDG-13| Climate Action| Carbon Farming, Agroforestry, Climate Resilience, MRV Systems
SDG-14| Life Below Water| Sustainable Aquaculture and Aquatic Ecosystem Management
SDG-15| Life on Land| Biodiversity Conservation, Ecosystem Restoration, Agroforestry
SDG-17| Partnerships for the Goals| Research Collaboration, Institutional Partnerships, Capacity Building

